ges to USAGE.md and only when there are actual discrepancies, I need to verify whether these code changes are already committed or still pending. I'm identifying the key factual errors to fix: the `--image` flag should be `--base-image`, and the default image should be `cloche-base:latest` instead of `ubuntu:24.04`. There are also some missing details in the docs about files created by init and the project directory layout, but I'll focus on these two clear discrepancies first since they're the most concrete issues.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":4696,"cache_read_input_tokens":66310,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":4696},"output_tokens":9,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"7bb04f91-48f6-482b-bb28-d1b340cab139","uuid":"8545fcf6-e59b-4d4a-9368-838156100e64"}
